## fallback positions

if independent claims rejected:

| scenario | fallback |
|----------|----------|
| claim 1 rejected | fall back to claim 2 (narrower) |
| claim 5 rejected | fall back to claim 6 (narrower) |
| all method claims rejected | pivot to system claims |

